title: Adobe InDesign CS4 portable with plugins
description:
Adobe InDesign CS4 6.0.1 Portable with most commercial plugins.
All plugins are time-limited trials but they work forever since that's a portable version.
Register all your settings, turn off unneeded plugins and backup the "Adobe InDesign CS4" folder. When the time has ended just restore these settings.
It's quick, compact, virus free and the plugins are powerful.
Please seed, even using the program in the same place.
